Sliders is a great neighborhood bar when it isn't game day and a great place to pregame before a game.

I was so impressed with this location, we were in town for a football game and were just looking for a place to watch the college games the night before. At first look, the size and look of the location would make you think it's just a place that serves a handful of beer choices and not much else. WRONG! They not only have those choices but they have local brewed choices as well as a great liquor selection. We had both chili cheese fries and the crab cake and chips. Both were great! In my opinion, does the place need newer furniture and TVs? Yes. But I'm not taking that away from them because I know many people like the older less modern feel of a bar. We obviously didn't mind it and certainly would consider returning the next time we are in Baltmore.
